                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d47">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">King of Italy</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-04-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 10, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>My countrymen are deeply impressed with awe and sorrow by the great calamity that
                    afflicts the Italian people in the disastrous eruption of Vesuvius. In their
                    name, and in my own, I tender to Your Majesty and the sufferers heartfelt
                    sympathy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Theodore Roosevelt.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
